Stanley Logan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stanley_Logan 0 Logan Stanley (born May 26, 1998) is a Canadian ice hockey defenceman who is currently with the Manitoba Moose of the American Hockey League (AHL) as a prospect to the Winnipeg Jets of the National Hockey League (NHL). Stanley was drafted 18th overall in the 2016 NHL Entry Draft by the Jets. He most recently played for the Kitchener Rangers of the Ontario Hockey League (OHL). Stanley was born in Kitchener, Ontario, but grew up in Waterloo, Ontario.
